1. Create a Resource Group
- Sign in to the Azure portal.
- Navigate to "Resource groups."
- Click "Create."
- Enter the Resource group name (e.g., EcommercePlatformRG).
- Choose the appropriate region.
- Click "Review + create" and then "Create."
